Attribute.value: This repository contains network and device indicators of compromised (IoCs) related to the IOS and Android spyware tools developed by the cyber-surveillance company Cytrox. These indicators were first published in December 2021 by Meta in their Threat Report on the Surveillance-for-Hire Industry and by Citizen Lab in their report Pegasus vs. Predator - Dissident’s Doubly-Infected iPhone Reveals Cytrox Mercenary Spyware. Additional indicators of compromise were identified by the Amnesty Tech Security Lab as part of an independent investigation.
